.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">119</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg009.perseus-grc1:792\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ra.\">Ra.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">792</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg063:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Herm.\">Herm.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">41</biblScope> </bibl> sq.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πρὸς βασιλέα τὸν μέγιστον ἔφεδρον ἀγωνιζόμεθα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:2:5:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.5.10</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">καθάπερ ἔ. ἀθλητῇ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg033:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sull.\">Sull.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">29</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Κράσσος, ὃς ἔ. ἦν ἀμφοῖν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg048:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Caes.\">Caes.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">28</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔ. τοῦ ἀγῶνος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg00